ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAddition to Tsinstikeptum Indian Reserve No. 10, British Columbia
PrecisOrder setting apart 0.27 hectare (0.67 acre) of land for the use and benefit of the Westbank First Nation as an addition to TSINSTIKEPTUM INDIAN RESERVE NO. 10, located in the District of West Kelowna at approximately 3.84 kilometres from the City of Kelowna, British Columbia.
